155
00:14:27,125 --> 00:14:28,084
Let him be.

156
00:14:30,987 --> 00:14:31,858
Hmm.

157
00:14:32,028 --> 00:14:33,732
Do I comprehend you?

158
00:14:33,815 --> 00:14:36,514
Let us clarify what you desire.

159
00:14:37,649 --> 00:14:40,739
Voluntarily you will give yourself to us

160
00:14:40,764 --> 00:14:43,648
