161
00:14:44,080 --> 00:14:45,516
Is that accurate?

162
00:14:52,333 --> 00:14:53,198
Yes.

163
00:14:53,528 --> 00:14:55,701
Only don't hurt my boy.

164
00:14:56,258 --> 00:14:58,068
You move me to tears.

165
00:14:58,208 --> 00:14:59,142
Agreed.

166
00:14:59,312 --> 00:15:01,079
